

imp-note

.js-lang is not a module based programming-lang till ES-5


 but in Node.js , we can make .js-modules using common-js standard.
 
 Node.js already implements common-js standard.
 
 
 common-js standard
 
 --> every .js file is an module by default
 --> all members are private to that module
 --> to export any member(s) to other modules , we shud use 'module.exports'
 --> to import module's memebers , we shud use 'require()'
 --> we can group related modules as package
 --> package can have descriptor file also ( package.json)
 
 
 -------------------------------------------------------------
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
